name: VOYU Passport for the NonNFT Summit 2022

metadata.name: VOYU Passport for the NonNFT Summit 2022
metadata.description: This passport includes: One (1) Commemorative Artwork NFT by XCopy, Moxarra and Neurocolor. One (1) Entry to the Summit. One (1) Free Access Pass to up to three (3) of VOYU's retreat's unique experiences during the week of Nov 7-11th.
